API : Application Programming Interface

URL = https://www.google.co.in/gmail

https : secure protocol
www.google.co.in : server address
/gmail : API end point

API Methods:
GET : retrieves the information or data from specific server
POST : submits the data to be processed to a specific server
DELETE :  Delete the record from specific server
PUT : update the specified information with new data.
PATCH : update the partial information of specific server

HTTP Response status code

100-  199 : Informational Response
200 - 299 : Successful response
300 - 399 : Redirection response message
400 - 499 : Client error response
500 - 502 : Server error response


